<h2 id="vocal-expression">Vocal expression</h2>
<p>
  When addressing a large set of users, don't be afraid to speak as if you were in the room. Users that are collated into one room should yield for the external user and be polite recognising time lag is an issue sometimes.
</p>
<p>
  Users MUST assume good intent when interacting with other users online.
</p>
<p>
  Be as clear as possible, audio equipment isn't always the most forgiving for people who tend to mumble.
</p>
